# @scholarpulse/web — Cloudflare Pages env

## Required for upstream Worker proxy

```bash
# Worker base URL (local dev or production)
SCHOLARPULSE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
```

When unset, web API routes fall back to in-memory stubs.

## Auth (optional — Supabase SSR)

```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR_PROJECT.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...
```

When both are set, `middleware.ts` uses `@supabase/ssr` to resolve `session.user.id`
and forwards it as `x-user-id` + `sp-user-id` cookie.

OAuth redirect target (configure in Supabase dashboard):

```text
https://YOUR_DOMAIN/auth/callback
```

## Auth gate (optional)

```bash
# 0 = public app sections allowed without login (default)
# 1 = protected routes redirect to /profile?auth=required
SP_REQUIRE_AUTH=0
```

Protected routes when `SP_REQUIRE_AUTH=1`:

- `/feed`, `/library`, `/notes`, `/statistics`, `/watch`, `/channels`
- `/profile`, `/settings`, `/desk`, `/user-report`, `/qc-report`
- `/` (desk home)

Public routes (always allowed):

- `/paper/*`, `/cite/*`, `/timeline/*`, `/search`, `/authors/*`, `/topics/*`
- `/login`, `/signin`, `/auth/*`, `/offline`

## SEO / site

```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://scholarpulse.example
```

## Local dev quick start

```bash
SCHOLARPULSE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787 corepack pnpm --filter @scholarpulse/web dev
```
